Why Shared Runners?

- Provided by GitLab
- Run on GitLab's infrastructure
- Easy to set up
- Limited customization
- Shared resources (CPU, memory) with other users
- Suitable for small projects or testing

why not Self-Hosted Runner for this project:

- Installed on your own infrastructure (on-premises or cloud)
- Run on your own machines or VMs
- More control and customization
- Dedicated resources (CPU, memory) for your pipelines
- Suitable for large projects, production environments, or high-security requirements
